          <title>Coby White, Torrey Craig lead the Bulls past the Hornets in overtime, 115-108</title>
          <description><![CDATA[Coby White narrowly missed his first career triple-double, finishing with 23 points, 10 rebounds and nine assists, and Torrey Craig scored 18 with five 3-pointers after halftime as the Chicago Bulls held on to beat the Charlotte Hornets 115-108 in overtime Monday night.]]></description>
